'''天主教孔塔戈拉教區'''（{{lang-en|Diocese of Kontagora}}）是[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教卡杜納總教區|卡杜納總教區]]。<ref name="Vatican20200402">{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 02.04.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/02/0197/00446.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-04-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403002626/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/02/0197/00446.html |archivedate=2020-04-03 |language=it |date=2020-04-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

'''孔塔戈拉宗座代牧區'''於1995年12月15日成立。<ref>{{cite web |title=KONTAGORANA* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19951215_kontagorana.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-04-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403034431/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19951215_kontagorana.html |archivedate=2020-04-03 |language=la |date=1995-12-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>宗座代牧區於2018年時有62788名教友（佔轄區人口2.7%）、17個堂區和35名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。宗座代牧區於2020年4月2日升為教區，管轄[[尼日爾州|尼日爾州]]和[[凱比州|凱比州]]，面積為46000[[平方公里|平方公里]]。<ref name="Vatican20200402" />現任教區主教為{{link-de|保祿·道瓦·約翰納|Bulus Dauwa Yohanna}}<ref name="Vatican20200402" />，榮休宗座代牧為{{link-en|弟茂德·卡羅爾 (主教)|Timothy Carroll (bishop)|弟茂德·卡羅爾}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 30.04.2010 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/04/30/0261/00606.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-04-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403041824/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/04/30/0261/00606.html |archivedate=2020-04-03 |language=it |date=2010-04-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

